a_Today|Russia Today]]|date=2014-04-13|accessdate=2020-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308155833/https://www.rt.com/news/ukraine-russia-operation-criminal-288/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過俄罗斯联邦也与顿涅茨克人民共和国政府保持距离，并且尚未承认它，<ref>{{cite web|title=Russia Uses Semantics To Walk Back Recognition of Donbass Elections Before G20 Summit|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/paulroderickgregory/2014/11/08/russia-uses-semantics-to-walk-back-recognition-of-donbass-elections-before-g20-summit/#323365b770a5|access-date=2016-06-03|last=Gregory|first=Paul Roderick|website=Forbes|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308043201/https://www.forbes.com/sites/paulroderickgregory/2014/11/08/russia-uses-semantics-to-walk-back-recognition-of-donbass-elections-before-g20-summit/#323365b770a5|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫曾多次就其政策发表明确声明，例如在顿涅茨克人民共和国部署国际维持和平特派团。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lavrov sees no perspective of deploying intl forces to Donbas|url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/347066.html|access-date=2016-06-03|website=Interfax-Ukraine|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224134407/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/347066.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
